description:
This is a 15 minute workout called '“GET STRONG” Best Core Exercises For Kids (15 Minute Kids Workout)' from the channel GVO Kids.
The workout falls under Cardio/Mat and Strength/Body weight.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Warrior Workout vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Today Vivien is leading a 15 Minute Kids Workout to get a strong core and body!  These are the best core exercises for kids to get better performance results! 

We hope you love these KIDS CORE EXERCISES TO GET STRONG! 

We put out new kids workouts every week - subscribe to our channel: @GVOKids
